Dialogs.Dialog: … Don't you get it？ You've been a little cold lately.
Huh？ I'm not in the mood.
I don't care if you're in a bad mood or not. You have to do better than that.
（Hmm. I have been in a bad mood today. I guess I've been a little cold lately.）
I'm sorry. It won't happen again！
… You're the one who's in the wrong, aren't you？
I can't help it. I'm your girlfriend, after all.
Hey, you should be in a better mood.
… Just this once. It's just this one time, so don't get carried away.
I know, I know！ I'm sorry！
（You forgave me, right？ I still don't think I'm satisfied, though…）
It's not what's going on with me. How are you doing lately？
Um… are you in a bad mood？
It's not Rinko's mood that sucks. It's your attitude that does.
（This is serious… I think I've been too cold lately…）
I'm so sorry！ It won't happen again！
… You're the one who's in the wrong, aren't you？
Why not？ It's okay. It's okay.
Hey, you need to get it together！
No, it's not going to happen.
I don't want to forgive… But I already have…
Forgive me！ I forgave you, right？…
（You forgave me, huh？ I don't think I'm satisfied…）
Is it just me, or have you been really cold lately？
Uh… I think you're just imagining things.
Please. Answer me one more time, correctly.
（Sounds like you're serious… It's true that I may have been rather cold lately…）
I'm so sorry！ It won't happen again！
… You're the one who's in the wrong, aren't you？
Because it doesn't make me less anxious…
Hey, you need to get it togehter.
… It can't be helped, can it？ If you're in a relationship for a long time, it happens…
Oh. They say it happens. So this is it's ugly face, huh？
Yeah… I guess so. And it can't be helped.
（You forgave me, right？ I don't think I'm quite satisfied with it…）
（▲小早川＊▲… are you still mad at me？）
Come on. Let's go home together.
（She might still be angry, I guess…）
（▲小早川＊▲… are you still mad at me？）
Come on. Let's go home together.
（She might still be angry, I guess…）
（▲小早川＊▲… are you still mad at me？）
Come on, let's go home together.
Rinko's not in the mood yet.
（She might still be angry, I guess…）
▲小早川＊▲. Let's go on a date.
▲小早川＊▲. You know, maybe we could…
▲小早川＊▲. Let's go on a date.
（A phone call？ ▲小早川＊▲… are you not mad at me anymore？）
（A phone call？ ▲小早川＊▲… are you not mad at me anymore？）
（A phone call？ ▲小早川＊▲… are you not mad at me anymore？）
Hey. I promised you a date. You remember, right？
Right. So I'm canceling that. See you later.
I can't see you now. Maybe you won't be able to see me after this, either…
Trying so hard. You look like an idiot.
Even in times like these, we don't cut corners.
Don't expect comfort out of me or anything.
（Oh, it's ▲小早川＊▲… Is she still mad at me？）
（Let's just leave it at that for now.）
（Oh, it's ▲小早川＊▲… Is she still mad at me？）
（Let's just leave it at that for now.）
（Oh, it's ▲小早川＊▲… Is she still mad at me？）
（Let's just leave it at that for now.）
Yeah. I know. I'm trying my best.
It's been too difficult to talk to ▲小早川＊▲ properly.
That's enough. I don't want to do this. I'm done.
Oh. I guess we'll make up.
… That's what you need to do.
I'm trying too hard. It's fine.
How can I get you to forgive me, ▲小早川＊▲？…
Your attitude has been too extreme. You have to just better yourself up in general.
Yeah. I've been reflecting on that.
It's okay. I've done enough to get even. It's been… pretty hard.
Oh, my God！ You idiot. Don't think I've just up and forgiven you for this.
I want to make up with you, ▲小早川＊▲ as soon as possible.
Yeah, thanks. Rinko's been at her wits' end.
It's natural. I was used to this before.
I'm sorry. I won't let you go through that again.
Huh？ Why…？ Well, come on in.
I just wanted to visit you. Have you been good？
What do you mean "have I been good"？ You came out of nowhere…
I've had enough. I got some time to myself, so it was perfect.
Well, I'm glad to hear it.
Sorry, I've been here for a while. I'd better get going.
That's not what I meant. But, thank you.
（I hope you feel better soon, ▲小早川＊▲.）
What？ Oh, hey！ … Okay, come on in.
You look like you're doing well.
Well, yeah. It was a bit over the top.
Am I bothering you at the moment？
You're not a bother. Thanks for going to the trouble of…
（This is kind of straightforward… Is it because of your illness？）
It's okay every once in a while. I'm really happy about it.
（Was that written all over my face？…）
Well, it's been a while. I'm about to leave. Can I come back？
You don't have to ask for everything you'd like to do.
（I hope you feel better soon, ▲小早川＊▲.）
What？ Don't come in here！ You can go to…
How are you doing？ You okay？
Yeah. I feel much better now. I was bored.
Yeah… Hehe. So, you're here to see me？
Of course I am. I was worried about you.
I should probably go home. I don't want to stay too long.
I don't want you to leave.
That's not how this works. You should get some rest and heal up some, first.
Okay… Will you come back some time？
Yeah. But you need rest now. I'll see you later.
（I hope you feel better soon, ▲小早川＊▲.）
But I can't leave my room.
Do something about it. Go talk to your mom.
Don't be selfish. You may look fine, but you're sick.
Hey. You've been visiting me a lot, but I wanted to know if you're free？
I'll come whether or not it's convenient.
Oh, shut up！ I'll see you later.
Are you really that worried about Rinko？ Do you want me to get better soon？
Well, of course. Why wouldn't I？
Well, that's a huge weight off my chest.
You're overreacting. It was just a cold, right？
It's hard enough to keep things from getting complicated. Just let me be honest and happy.
I can't help it. You're such an old man and a worrywart.
Haha. Yeah. I'm fully back up to my normal self.
Also, thank for for your concern and help.
Hmm？ Oh. Don't worry about it. I'm just glad you're better.
I'll leave you to your business again. I just wanted to let you know I was happy to see you.
Yeah. It's all because of you visiting me and caring for me, right？
Haha. Oh, yeah？ ▲小早川＊▲ was also pretty quiet.
Because, you know, I wanted to get back to playing.
But you know what？ I want to start with you first.
（I'm pretty bored… I'm tired of being secluded to home.）
Yeah, I want to visit. I'm your girlfriend, after all.
Thank you, but I don't want to get you sick.
I don't care if you're sick.
Haha. But I'm glad you came. I had some free time.
Oh, it's late. I'd better be going.
You can come over again, okay？
I'd like to, but… I need you to heal, not get worse.
You should get well soon. You're not the only one who's bored because you're sick.
（For ▲小早川＊▲'s sake I have to get well soon.）
（I'm pretty bored… I'm tired of being secluded to home.）
This is what you'd call… sympathy？
I was surprised. I didn't think you'd come.
Wy would that be so unexpected？
It wasn't unexpected, just so sudden.
I thought it would be more gratifying. Anyway, I'm glad you're doing well.
I'd better get going. You need rest.
And I'm taking care of you because you're sick and weak.
That's right. I don't think I'm the one that needs worried about. It's you who's sick, right？
（For ▲小早川＊▲'s sake I have to get well soon.）
（I'm pretty bored… I'm tired of being secluded to home.）
Hehe. I'm here. Is that okay？
I had some free time. I'm glad you came.
I'm getting there. It's getting easier to do stuff.
I'm sorry. I stayed too long. I'll go home now.
Oh, thank you. You really helped me.
Is there anything else you need help with？ Like any housework？
Oh, you're fine. I wouldn't put you to work like that.
… Don't look so anxious. If it gets really bad, give me a call. I'll see you later.
（For ▲小早川＊▲'s sake I have to get well soon.）
Hey. Is Rinko interrupting you or anything？
No way. I'm glad you're here.
Hmm. This is a nice privilege of being a boyfriend.
You know, you're a lucky guy. Not everyone's girlfriend comes to see them when they're sick.
Oh, I am a lucky man. I have no regrets…
Don't you feel convicted for saying something like that in this situation？
I don't care. Even if the roles were reversed, I could still kick your butt.
So, what do you want to do？
Well, you're here. And a kiss could make me… feel better.？
Yeah, no. Not until you're healed.
If you're so frustrated, get some rest and sleep the sickness off.
Thank you for your sympathy. Thanks to you, I'm back.
That's not much of a reaction.
I'm sour because I was left to my own boredom for too long. Next time just don't get sick.
Thanks to you, I'm back to full strength！ Try and kick me now, I can dodge it！
Ouch！ That had some feeling behind it.
Don't worry about Rinko when you're sick！
I'm all better now and it's all because ▲小早川＊▲ came to visit and check on me.
Hehe. you got it！ Now as payment, you need to take me out on a date.
Hey, hey. When do you want to do it？
